If Mikoy really loves you,
he'll accept you for who you are.

11
00:01:02,187 --> 00:01:03,396
<i>Whoever you may be.</i>

12
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:05,398
What if the person betrays you?

13
00:01:05,482 --> 00:01:06,816
Would he still be called a snake?

14
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:08,526
