15
00:01:08,610 --> 00:01:10,278
You're betraying me, aren't you?

16
00:01:10,361 --> 00:01:14,074
<i>I strongly believe that Chiara</i>
<i>has something to do with the Moraviano.</i>

17
00:01:14,157 --> 00:01:16,951
