So if they can throw a party
this big and this extravagant,

36
00:02:51,379 --> 00:02:54,382
it creates the impression
that they are completely legit.

37
00:02:55,174 --> 00:02:58,553
So this Vertex event is telling the public

38
00:02:59,053 --> 00:03:00,930
