is ready to do business.

39
00:03:07,103 --> 00:03:07,979
Exactly!

40
00:03:08,062 --> 00:03:11,232
That's why this is the perfect opportunity
to have eyes and ears on the ground.

41
00:03:16,529 --> 00:03:17,572
Oh!

42
00:03:18,156 --> 00:03:19,866
Sorry, I'm late.

43
00:03:21,534 --> 00:03:22,744
Snacks.

44
