99
00:06:39,649 --> 00:06:40,817
Oh, right.

100
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:42,401
Here's the invitation.

101
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,795
So who exactly is Viktor Valtrovi?

102
00:07:00,878 --> 00:07:06,926
He is an ultra-rich Czech citizen
who's been the talk of elite circles.

103
00:07:07,009 --> 00:07:09,929
They say he plans to invest
and transfer all his wealth

104
