Viktor fell in love
and married a true-blue Filipina.

107
00:07:20,773 --> 00:07:23,526
Notorious as someone
with expert-level beauty.

108
00:07:23,609 --> 00:07:26,070
Hailing from Mabalacat, Pampanga,

109
00:07:26,154 --> 00:07:30,324
Mrs. Valtrovi a.k.a. Donabel.

110
00:07:30,408 --> 00:07:33,286
We have another fellow Filipino
who made it in life.

111
00:07:33,369 --> 00:07:35,788
This is really who everyone
has been waiting for.

112
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:41,085
Their only daughter.

113
00:07:41,169 --> 00:07:46,382
