123
00:08:52,949 --> 00:08:54,158
Uh…

124
00:08:55,493 --> 00:08:58,538
Good evening to all of you.

125
00:08:59,539 --> 00:09:05,378
I am Michael "Mikoy" D. Pinagpala.

126
00:09:07,505 --> 00:09:10,466
Did you know that when I was a child,

127
