Do you see it, too?

152
00:11:48,416 --> 00:11:49,625
<i>Nice!</i>

153
00:11:49,708 --> 00:11:52,545
This isn't just an ordinary
rich people party.

154
00:11:52,628 --> 00:11:54,338
Better than the United Nations.

155
00:11:54,422 --> 00:11:56,507
There's diversity.

156
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:58,592
There's even inclusivity.

157
