159
00:12:14,442 --> 00:12:18,195
Because he owns thousands
of vape shops in the Philippines.

160
00:12:24,243 --> 00:12:26,704
They own "Sana All Glow".

161
00:12:26,787 --> 00:12:31,000
A skincare brand loved by Gen Zs.

162
00:12:35,129 --> 00:12:37,715
<i>Lebron James!</i>

163
00:12:40,468 --> 00:12:42,136
Former MVP on the court.

164
00:12:42,219 --> 00:12:44,305
Now an all-around producer

165
00:12:44,388 --> 00:12:48,767
