166
00:12:48,851 --> 00:12:50,311
Where's that cake already?

167
00:12:50,394 --> 00:12:51,395
Where is it?

168
00:12:51,479 --> 00:12:53,063
Serve the food already!

169
00:12:53,564 --> 00:12:55,733
We can't refill anything there anymore.
Why is it only coming out now?

170
00:12:55,816 --> 00:12:57,776
-Sorry, Chef.
-Go ahead. Bring it out.

171
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:04,116
<i>Hello, Engineer. Ready for fumigation.</i>

172
00:13:58,379 --> 00:14:01,465
the new global Czech charmer stud.

173
00:14:01,549 --> 00:14:03,384
Sir Viktor Valtrovi!

174
00:14:05,761 --> 00:14:08,305
our very own Filipina beauty represents,

175
00:14:08,389 --> 00:14:11,475
the incredible Donabel!

176
00:14:33,539 --> 00:14:35,541
Nothing so far, Mother Eagle.

177
00:14:35,624 --> 00:14:40,087
But if Viktor and Donabel
have a production number,

178
00:14:40,921 --> 00:14:44,008
then surely, there's also
a production number

179
00:14:44,508 --> 00:14:45,676
for Mikoy and Chiara.

180
00:14:45,759 --> 00:14:47,219
<i>And that's what I'm looking for.</i>

181
00:15:14,121 --> 00:15:16,749
<i>Maybe it's nothing.</i>
<i>Just someone who fell asleep</i>

182
00:15:16,832 --> 00:15:17,875
and ended up lying there.

183
00:15:17,958 --> 00:15:19,668
How about this? I'll go down.

184
00:15:19,752 --> 00:15:22,087
Eagle 3, we need to stick
to our game plan, okay?

185
00:15:22,171 --> 00:15:25,883
But our game plan is to stay alert
for whatever might happen.

186
00:15:25,966 --> 00:15:28,886
That's why you have to stick
and stay alert at your post.

187
00:15:39,563 --> 00:15:41,148
What the--

188
00:16:25,109 --> 00:16:26,777
Code 10-7? Why, who died?

189
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:27,820
The security guards.

190
00:16:27,903 --> 00:16:29,321
Looks like they were the first casualties.

191
00:16:29,405 --> 00:16:32,574
So if someone got past
the Moraviano security…

192
00:16:33,117 --> 00:16:35,577
That means the enemy is inside.

193
00:17:23,459 --> 00:17:25,711
We can handle this.
We are already in the middle of a mission.

194
00:17:26,837 --> 00:17:29,256
It's natural that all factors
are working against us.

195
00:17:29,339 --> 00:17:31,425
Mother Eagle, we're unprepared, okay?

196
00:17:31,508 --> 00:17:33,886
I don't want to risk all your lives. Okay?

197
00:17:35,137 --> 00:17:37,389
-That's part of our job.
-<i>Exactly.</i>

198
00:17:37,473 --> 00:17:40,267
Looks like I still have eight lives left.

199
00:17:40,350 --> 00:17:42,603
-I'll make the most of it.
-Eagle 3!

200
00:17:46,065 --> 00:17:47,566
What about Mikoy?

201
00:17:48,901 --> 00:17:50,027
And the Pinagpalas?

202
00:17:53,238 --> 00:17:55,074
<i>We can't just back out.</i>

203
00:17:55,908 --> 00:17:58,577
If the enemies got past
the Moraviano security,

204
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:00,579
that means they're here at the party,

205
00:18:01,497 --> 00:18:03,457
dressed up and clapping.

206
00:18:03,540 --> 00:18:05,834
But just like us,
they're pretending and waiting.

207
00:18:22,226 --> 00:18:27,356
Mr. Michael "Mikoy" Pinagpala!

208
00:18:50,129 --> 00:18:53,423
<i>Michael "Mikoy" D. Pinagpala.</i>

209
00:19:06,728 --> 00:19:07,563
Uh…

210
00:19:09,148 --> 00:19:10,858
Good evening to all of you.

211
00:19:10,941 --> 00:19:14,862
My name is Michael "Mikoy" D. Pinagpala.

212
00:19:15,696 --> 00:19:18,657
You know, when I was a kid,
I was often teased about whether

213
00:19:19,241 --> 00:19:20,659
we were really "blessed".

214
00:19:21,368 --> 00:19:24,997
Because honestly, with all
the hardships our family went through,

215
00:19:25,581 --> 00:19:27,166
you can't really blame them.

216
00:19:27,916 --> 00:19:30,085
Even I started to wonder.

217
00:19:30,169 --> 00:19:31,086
It made me think,

218
00:19:31,712 --> 00:19:33,422
are we really blessed?

219
00:19:33,505 --> 00:19:34,756
But you know,

220
00:19:35,257 --> 00:19:37,551
no matter where life takes me,

221
00:19:37,634 --> 00:19:39,469
no matter where I end up,

222
00:19:39,553 --> 00:19:43,390
whether in Quiapo, Boljoon, or Prague,

223
00:19:43,473 --> 00:19:45,184
<i>in the end,</i>

224
00:19:45,851 --> 00:19:47,728
<i>I still made it to this very stage,</i>

225
00:19:47,811 --> 00:19:49,313
standing before all of you

226
00:19:49,396 --> 00:19:52,691
as the new COO of Vertex Global.

227
00:19:59,114 --> 00:20:01,408
And I'm ready. I'm fully prepared.

228
00:20:01,491 --> 00:20:04,369
Of course, there's a bit of nervousness.

229
00:20:04,453 --> 00:20:08,957
But what I feel more strongly is,

230
00:20:09,583 --> 00:20:11,126
that yes,

231
00:20:12,002 --> 00:20:13,587
I truly am blessed.

232
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:16,924
I am blessed with the love and guidance.

233
00:20:17,007 --> 00:20:19,384
Mom… Dad…

234
00:20:21,303 --> 00:20:22,804
Thank you so much.

235
00:20:24,264 --> 00:20:26,808
For all the sacrifices you made for me.

236
00:20:27,434 --> 00:20:28,727
I love you.

237
00:20:30,812 --> 00:20:32,356
And not just that.

238
00:20:32,856 --> 00:20:37,236
I am also blessed with the trust
and support you've given me.

239
00:20:37,319 --> 00:20:40,280
Papa Viktor, Mama Donabel,

240
00:20:41,156 --> 00:20:42,783
thank you so much.

241
00:20:43,283 --> 00:20:46,245
I will try my best as much as I can.

242
00:20:46,328 --> 00:20:48,247
I won't let you down.

243
00:20:48,872 --> 00:20:51,375
You know, I've never won the lottery.

244
00:20:52,042 --> 00:20:56,672
But maybe this is what it feels like
to hit the jackpot.

245
00:20:59,508 --> 00:21:03,512
Chiara. You are the greatest blessing
that has come into my life.

246
00:21:05,097 --> 00:21:06,473
I just want you to know

247
00:21:07,224 --> 00:21:08,934
that I will do everything for you.

248
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:11,645
Whatever needs to be done.

249
00:21:13,897 --> 00:21:15,482
Whatever is right.

250
00:21:17,484 --> 00:21:18,819
For everyone.

251
00:21:22,072 --> 00:21:24,324
Chiara, just don't ever forget

252
00:21:25,701 --> 00:21:28,954
that I love you so, so much.

253
00:21:35,002 --> 00:21:37,045
That's all. Thank you very, very much.

254
00:21:43,427 --> 00:21:44,469
Mikoy!

255
00:21:53,770 --> 00:21:54,646
Wait.

256
00:21:54,730 --> 00:21:56,189
<i>Three o'clock!</i>

257
00:22:12,414 --> 00:22:13,957
It's over for you.

258
00:22:15,334 --> 00:22:17,586
Honey, I really need to pee.

259
00:22:17,669 --> 00:22:19,921
-I can't hold it anymore.
-Come with me.

260
00:22:20,005 --> 00:22:21,590
-Right now?
-Yes.

261
00:22:21,673 --> 00:22:23,550
-Come with me.
-Sure, sure.

262
00:22:25,927 --> 00:22:26,762
We'll be back.

263
00:22:26,845 --> 00:22:29,181
-All the sacrifices you made.
-We'll come back.

264
00:22:29,890 --> 00:22:31,516
All the times you held back.

265
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:36,855
From doing things for yourself
because you always put others first.

266
00:22:37,355 --> 00:22:41,151
All of that is what brought you here.

267
00:22:41,234 --> 00:22:43,612
You'd better just cooperate with us.

268
00:22:43,695 --> 00:22:45,864
And don't add
to your failed murder attempt.

269
00:22:46,490 --> 00:22:49,618
Because you have a big, big heart.

270
00:23:19,272 --> 00:23:21,149
You can't stop me.

271
00:23:29,157 --> 00:23:31,868
Mr. Michael "Mikoy" Pinagpala.

272
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:49,553
Mother Eagle. Mother Eagle,
there are many of them!

273
00:24:08,905 --> 00:24:11,116
Chiara!

274
00:24:12,492 --> 00:24:13,785
-You go ahead first!
-Chiara!

275
00:24:31,469 --> 00:24:34,306
-Mikoy, you'll survive, son!
-You can do it, Mikoy.

276
00:24:34,389 --> 00:24:36,308
-Let's wait here.
-My son!

277
00:24:36,391 --> 00:24:37,809
Brace yourself.

278
00:24:37,893 --> 00:24:40,228
Your brother Mikoy is in the hospital.

279
00:24:40,312 --> 00:24:41,313
He got shot.

280
00:24:43,565 --> 00:24:44,941
How's Mikoy? Where is he?

281
00:24:45,525 --> 00:24:47,611
<i>I heard from the ER</i>
<i>there's a gunshot victim.</i>

282
00:24:51,114 --> 00:24:52,490
<i>They took your mother.</i>

283
00:24:52,574 --> 00:24:53,658
Viktor!

284
00:24:57,037 --> 00:25:00,582
Do you think what your husband
did to us is funny?

285
00:25:02,834 --> 00:25:04,211
<i>like a conquering hero.</i>

286
00:25:04,294 --> 00:25:08,256
<i>He built the Moraviano</i>
<i>without advice or permission.</i>

287
00:25:09,466 --> 00:25:11,301
<i>Your husband ruined everything.</i>

288
00:25:11,384 --> 00:25:14,054
<i>Not only properties, but many families!</i>

289
00:25:14,137 --> 00:25:15,847
<i>For what? To be a tyrant?</i>

290
00:25:15,931 --> 00:25:17,515
You're just a criminal.

291
00:25:17,599 --> 00:25:20,101
You got outsmarted by a criminal
who's better than you.

292
00:25:20,185 --> 00:25:21,686
He's my husband.

293
00:25:26,983 --> 00:25:30,362
<i>And I will make whoever</i>
<i>did this to Mikoy pay.</i>

294
00:25:30,362 --> 00:25:31,362
MkvDrama.net

